message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product, which is valued at $150 to me due to its unique features and high-quality materials. Considering its worth and the benefits it provides, I believe we can come to an agreement that satisfies both of us. I am proposing to sell the product to you for $120. This offer allows you to enjoy significant savings while ensuring a fair transaction for me. I look forward to your positive response.
